A
B\supset A
m^*(B\setminus A)=m^*(B)-m(A)
m^*(B)=m^*(B\cap A)+m^*(B\setminus A)\overset?=m(A)+m^*(B\setminus A)
m^*(B\cap A)=m(A)
A \subset B \implies A= B \cap A
